sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant W as 🔌 Chat Widget
    participant C as ⚡ Caddy
    participant F as 🚀 FastAPI
    participant MW as 🔐 Auth Middleware
    participant CS as 💬 Chat Service
    participant DB as 🐘 PostgreSQL
    participant CR as 🔮 ChromaDB
    participant LM as 🤖 Gemini / Ollama
    participant RD as ⚡ Redis
    participant LK as 📋 Loki

    U->>W: Types message
    W->>C: POST /api/v1/chat/public
    C->>F: Proxy request (TLS terminated)
    F->>MW: Validate X-API-Key header
    MW->>F: tenant_id extracted
    F->>LK: Log: chat_request_received

    F->>DB: Get or Create Conversation
    F->>DB: INSERT user message

    alt Small Talk Match
        F->>DB: Check bot.small_talk_responses
        F-->>W: Return cached small talk response
    else Agent Transfer Keywords
        F->>DB: Check transfer_trigger_keywords
        F->>DB: Mark conversation status = open
        F-->>W: Return transfer message
    else RAG + AI Response
        F->>DB: Fetch chat history (last 11 messages)
        F->>CR: Vector similarity search (query embedding)
        CR-->>F: Top-K relevant documents + scores
        F->>LM: LLM call with context + history + query
        LM-->>F: Generated answer
        F->>DB: INSERT bot message
        F->>RD: Increment tenant usage counter
    end

    F->>LK: Log: ai_response_generated with duration_ms
    F-->>C: JSON ChatResponse
    C-->>W: HTTPS Response
    W-->>U: Display answer with sources and quick replies
